### ===== ТЕСТЫ ВАЛИДАЦИИ =====

### 6. name пустой (minLength: 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "Описание",
  "price": 100.00,
  "stock": 5,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 7. name слишком длинный (maxLength: 255)
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA",
  "description": "Описание",
  "price": 100.00,
  "stock": 5,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 8. price отрицательный (minimum: 0.01)
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Товар",
  "description": "Описание",
  "price": -5.00,
  "stock": 5,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 9. price = 0 (minimum: 0.01)
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Товар",
  "description": "Описание",
  "price": 1,
  "stock": 1,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 10. stock отрицательный (minimum: 0)
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Товар",
  "description": "Описание",
  "price": 100.00,
  "stock": -3,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 11. category пустая (minLength: 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Товар",
  "description": "Описание",
  "price": 100.00,
  "stock": 5,
  "category": "",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 12. status невалидный (enum: ACTIVE, INACTIVE, ARCHIVED)
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Товар",
  "description": "Описание",
  "price": 100.00,
  "stock": 5,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "status": "DELETED"
}

### 13. отсутствует обязательное поле name
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Описание",
  "price": 100.00,
  "stock": 5,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 14. отсутствует несколько обязательных полей
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Товар"
}

### 15. пустое тело запроса
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 16. невалидный JSON
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{не json вообще}

### 17. лишнее поле (additionalProperties: false)
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Товар",
  "price": 100.00,
  "stock": 5,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "hacker_field": "ха-ха"
}

### 18. невалидный page в query (minimum: 0)
GET http://localhost:8080/products?page=-1&size=5
Accept: application/json

### 19. невалидный size в query (minimum: 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/products?page=0&size=0
Accept: application/json

### 20. невалидный UUID в path
GET http://localhost:8080/products/not-a-uuid
Accept: application/json

### 21. валидация PUT — те же правила
PUT http://localhost:8080/products/{{product_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "price": -1,
  "stock": -5,
  "category": "",
  "status": "WRONG"
}

### 22. description слишком длинный (maxLength: 4000) — строка из 4001 символа
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Товар",
  "description": "
